spec_data.Name: texlive-grfpaste
spec_data.Description:
Provides a mechanism to include fragments of dvi files with the
graphicx package, so that you can use \includegraphics to
include dvi files. The package requires the dvipaste program.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 08:19:48 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Include fragments of a dvi file
